data.description: Opportunity knocks - ACT FAST!!! This beautiful fully remodeled 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is not going to last! Wood plank tile flooring throughout with rugs in the bedrooms. Bathrooms have been fully updated with subway tile and top of the line fixtures. The kitchen is gorgeous with dove tail REAL pine cabinets with spice racks, new stainless steel appliances, fixtures......a true Chef's kitchen! Brand new roof, oversized lot with more than enough room for resort style pool.....this is the ultimate dream home with opportunity to make it your own! All offers must be submitted by January 22nd at 5:00 pm.
